WEBVTT

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:34.940
[The Unclouded Soul]

00:01:35.170 --> 00:01:37.860
[Episode 31]
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:01:38.020 --> 00:01:38.570
Hong Ye,

00:01:39.330 --> 00:01:40.950
you thought sealing us away
for 10,000 years

00:01:40.950 --> 00:01:42.840
would allow you to seize power alone?

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:44.640
Today, I'll show you what it feels like

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:45.820
to die 1,000 deaths.

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.180
I'd like to peel off his skin,

00:01:49.490 --> 00:01:50.890
stuff it with his hair,

00:01:51.120 --> 00:01:52.479
and make it a ball to play with.
Sounds good?

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:53.680
That's too merciful.

00:01:55.310 --> 00:01:57.370
I want to strip the flesh from his body

00:01:57.710 --> 00:01:59.280
piece by piece,

00:02:00.070 --> 00:02:02.130
each slice as thin as a cicada's wing.

00:02:02.560 --> 00:02:03.890
Both of you, stand down.

00:02:04.150 --> 00:02:05.710
Just watch.

00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:06.510
Ao Hen!

00:02:07.150 --> 00:02:08.400
We all suffered the seal for 10,000 years.

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:09.680
What right do you have to act alone?

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:10.190
Shut up.

00:02:36.590 --> 00:02:37.750
Redirect the formation

00:02:37.750 --> 00:02:39.430
to focus the attack 15 miles southwest.

00:02:39.430 --> 00:02:40.690
Change the formation!

00:02:58.610 --> 00:02:59.730
Die in battle,

00:03:00.070 --> 00:03:03.600
and at least your family will
receive compensation to live off.

00:03:03.630 --> 00:03:06.290
But desertion is
defying His Majesty's orders.

00:03:07.260 --> 00:03:09.060
You will be killed with no mercy.

00:03:18.010 --> 00:03:18.780
Ao Hen,

00:03:18.920 --> 00:03:19.630
here's the thing.

00:03:19.630 --> 00:03:20.760
You hit way too hard.

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:21.600
A move of yours

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:22.710
will reduce him to ashes, right?

00:03:22.710 --> 00:03:23.370
Let go of me!

00:03:23.730 --> 00:03:24.590
We'd better...

00:03:24.630 --> 00:03:25.560
I'll be gentler.

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:26.700
Let me go first!

00:03:27.520 --> 00:03:29.160
You are even more brutal.

00:03:29.480 --> 00:03:30.530
Let me do this.

00:04:11.940 --> 00:04:14.820
♪ A thousand years have flowed by ♪

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:18.440
♪ Turning into tears
that brim over my eyes ♪

00:04:18.560 --> 00:04:19.810
I've seen everything.

00:04:19.810 --> 00:04:22.120
♪ And the moonlight to heal sorrow ♪

00:04:22.120 --> 00:04:23.400
And I've experienced everything.

00:04:23.400 --> 00:04:26.120
♪ The sweetness of the world
always tastes like the first time ♪

00:04:26.260 --> 00:04:27.160
Now I understand your suffering.

00:04:27.160 --> 00:04:30.120
♪ The joys and sorrows in my dreams ♪

00:04:30.120 --> 00:04:31.390
The agony from the past is
hidden deep down inside.

00:04:31.390 --> 00:04:33.830
♪ Transformed into a farewell song,
stirring the soul ♪

00:04:33.830 --> 00:04:35.060
All I want now is you.

00:04:35.060 --> 00:04:37.200
♪ And into wind and rain,
drifting and swirling ♪

00:04:37.200 --> 00:04:37.870
Xiao Yao.

00:04:38.710 --> 00:04:40.190
♪ The ship of fate
always faces the waves ♪

00:04:40.190 --> 00:04:42.150
I have been waiting for you all this time.

00:04:42.150 --> 00:04:45.080
♪ From now on, someone will share
all my love and hatred ♪

00:04:45.750 --> 00:04:46.140
I am Xiao Yao.

00:04:46.140 --> 00:04:48.460
♪ Together, we explore
mountains and rivers with one heart ♪

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:49.500
And I am also Ning'an.

00:04:49.500 --> 00:04:51.850
♪ From now on, someone will share
all my dreams and my drinks ♪

00:04:51.850 --> 00:04:52.980
It's always been me.

00:04:53.820 --> 00:04:55.750
♪ With an extra pair of eyes, we
admire the sun, moon, and stars together ♪

00:04:55.750 --> 00:04:56.430
Hong Ye,

00:04:57.080 --> 00:04:58.090
♪ From now on, the moon fears waning,
the waves long for the returning tide ♪

00:04:58.090 --> 00:04:58.920
I'm sorry.

00:05:01.330 --> 00:05:03.250
♪ I carry an extra touch of care
in my heart and on my brow ♪

00:05:03.250 --> 00:05:04.690
Back then,
I was constrained by circumstances

00:05:04.690 --> 00:05:06.120
♪ From now on,
with reckless courage and mutual longing ♪

00:05:06.120 --> 00:05:07.480
and could not tell you

00:05:08.560 --> 00:05:09.250
that my love for you was true.

00:05:09.250 --> 00:05:12.410
♪ We forsake three lifetimes of marriage,
only to fulfill our wishes ♪

00:05:12.410 --> 00:05:15.010
In this life,
I am no longer the human princess.

00:05:23.320 --> 00:05:25.780
Your return alone is
the greatest blessing.

00:05:35.630 --> 00:05:38.460
♪ From now on, the moon fears waning,
the waves long for the returning tide ♪

00:05:39.670 --> 00:05:41.290
♪ I carry an extra touch of care
in my heart and on my brow ♪

00:05:41.290 --> 00:05:42.060
See that?

00:05:42.820 --> 00:05:43.110
This woman is human,

00:05:43.110 --> 00:05:44.570
♪ From now on,
with reckless courage and mutual longing ♪

00:05:44.570 --> 00:05:45.830
in league with Hong Ye,

00:05:46.190 --> 00:05:47.100
full of tricks.

00:05:47.700 --> 00:05:52.670
♪ We forsake three lifetimes of marriage,
only to fulfill our wishes ♪

00:05:54.270 --> 00:05:56.670
I've brought back your primordial spirit.

00:05:58.560 --> 00:05:59.760
I'll return it to you.

