00:06:40.580 --> 00:06:42.970
♪ With an extra pair of eyes, we
admire the sun, moon, and stars together ♪

00:06:43.840 --> 00:06:47.190
♪ From now on, the moon fears waning,
the waves long for the returning tide ♪

00:06:48.080 --> 00:06:50.620
♪ I carry an extra touch of care
in my heart and on my brow ♪

00:06:51.450 --> 00:06:54.760
♪ From now on,
with reckless courage and mutual longing ♪

00:06:56.010 --> 00:07:01.410
♪ Giving up three lives of marriage
just for ♪

00:07:05.580 --> 00:07:07.080
♪ Our wishes ♪

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:17.350
Let go of my sister!

00:07:30.030 --> 00:07:30.740
Xiao Yao!

00:07:31.830 --> 00:07:32.360
It's you?

00:07:32.640 --> 00:07:33.700
What are you doing?

00:07:34.659 --> 00:07:35.920
Don't you remember me?

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:37.080
Stay back!

00:07:38.750 --> 00:07:40.430
Why is your power weaker than before?

00:07:40.430 --> 00:07:41.170
Are you sick?

00:07:41.190 --> 00:07:42.120
Let me check on you.

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:42.680
Say whatever you want,

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:43.800
but don't touch me!

00:07:44.040 --> 00:07:44.580
Hands off her!

00:07:44.580 --> 00:07:46.240
You don't remember anything?

00:07:47.220 --> 00:07:48.550
It's been 10,000 years,

00:07:48.610 --> 00:07:49.940
and you still don't know

00:07:49.940 --> 00:07:51.390
who truly cares for you.

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:57.570
What are you talking about?

00:07:59.650 --> 00:08:00.340
Sister!

00:08:18.300 --> 00:08:18.830
Xiao Yao,

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:19.630
run!

00:08:50.390 --> 00:08:50.990
Hong Ye,

00:08:51.390 --> 00:08:52.390
if you dare lay a finger on her,

00:08:52.390 --> 00:08:53.780
I swear I will tear you to pieces!

00:08:53.780 --> 00:08:55.120
If you try to bewitch her again,

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:56.750
I'll make you die
an even more miserable death!

00:08:56.750 --> 00:08:57.750
You despicable rascal!

00:08:57.750 --> 00:08:58.810
Stay away from her!

00:09:00.900 --> 00:09:02.190
How do they know us?

00:09:03.430 --> 00:09:04.700
You know us?

00:09:04.800 --> 00:09:05.330
-Mm.
-Mm.

00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:07.260
What's my name?

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:08.560
-Xiao Yao.
-Xiao Yao.

00:09:10.290 --> 00:09:11.750
Hong Ye just called it out.

00:09:12.390 --> 00:09:13.180
Who are you?

00:09:13.450 --> 00:09:14.650
I'm Qiong Qi.

00:09:15.720 --> 00:09:17.030
I'm your big brother!

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:19.540
Qiong Qi?

00:09:19.970 --> 00:09:21.310
My big brother?

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:29.810
Do you remember me then?

00:09:30.860 --> 00:09:32.120
Do you remember Ao Hen?

00:09:33.660 --> 00:09:35.150
You're Ao Hen?

00:09:39.030 --> 00:09:39.630
Sister!

00:09:40.510 --> 00:09:41.030
Me...

00:09:43.900 --> 00:09:46.270
You couldn't be Teng She, could you?

00:09:48.080 --> 00:09:49.600
Sister remembers me! She remembers me!

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:50.770
After 10,000 years,

00:09:50.910 --> 00:09:53.130
she only remembers me.

00:09:56.510 --> 00:09:57.440
Hold on, hold on.

00:09:58.200 --> 00:09:58.750
I

00:09:58.880 --> 00:10:00.030
have a poor memory.

00:10:00.030 --> 00:10:01.220
I really don't remember

00:10:01.220 --> 00:10:02.750
how we met.

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:04.530
Xiao Yao,

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:06.170
it's been 10,000 years.

00:10:06.170 --> 00:10:08.080
Who knows how many times
of reincarnation you've had?

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:09.790
It's just normal
that you don't remember clearly.

00:10:09.790 --> 00:10:11.590
But she still remembers Hong Ye.

00:11:03.320 --> 00:11:04.450
Three great demons,

00:11:04.760 --> 00:11:06.670
our demon kind is teetering
on the brink of destruction.

00:11:06.670 --> 00:11:08.360
Whatever grievances or grudges you have,

00:11:08.360 --> 00:11:09.910
please cast them aside for now.

00:11:09.910 --> 00:11:11.250
For nearly 10,000 years,

00:11:11.250 --> 00:11:13.420
our demon kind
has been through countless catastrophes,

00:11:13.420 --> 00:11:14.820
with few of us remaining.

00:11:14.910 --> 00:11:16.220
How dare you say that?

00:11:17.120 --> 00:11:17.550
You 3,

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:19.890
you possess such immense power

00:11:19.890 --> 00:11:21.750
just to harm your own kind?

00:11:25.120 --> 00:11:25.720
Yes.

00:11:27.670 --> 00:11:28.390
Of course.

00:11:31.150 --> 00:11:32.720
The Demons' Valley beneath your feet is

00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:33.960
the only place in this world

00:11:33.960 --> 00:11:35.300
for demons to inhabit.

00:11:35.630 --> 00:11:36.830
It's in danger now.

00:11:36.910 --> 00:11:38.570
It's fine if you don't help us.

00:11:38.600 --> 00:11:40.150
But please, at least let us out
to defend it.

00:11:40.150 --> 00:11:41.790
Whatever issues you have,
we can discuss them when we return.

00:11:41.790 --> 00:11:42.520
Is that okay?

00:11:44.950 --> 00:11:47.150
Can't believe demons have become so weak,

00:11:47.150 --> 00:11:48.790
being cornered by humans to this extent.

00:11:48.790 --> 00:11:50.120
Just some minor humans.

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:50.770
Xiao Yao,

00:11:51.200 --> 00:11:52.600
I'll help you solve this.

00:11:54.840 --> 00:11:56.200
As long as you ask, Sister,

00:11:56.200 --> 00:11:58.840
I'll do anything for you.

00:12:03.550 --> 00:12:04.280
Don't worry,

00:12:04.550 --> 00:12:05.350
I'm here, too.

00:12:11.320 --> 00:12:11.820
Deer!

00:12:14.910 --> 00:12:15.790
Bamboo!

00:12:20.120 --> 00:12:22.580
Please don't let me be a broom
in my next life!

00:12:47.080 --> 00:12:48.010
Don't be afraid.

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:18.910
What are you doing?

00:13:18.910 --> 00:13:19.390
Attack!

00:13:19.820 --> 00:13:21.520
Such a soft little kitty like you

00:13:21.520 --> 00:13:22.920
should be playing with yarn balls

00:13:22.920 --> 00:13:24.380
instead of fighting here.

00:13:25.630 --> 00:13:26.570
Leave this to me.

00:14:14.030 --> 00:14:15.880
Can believe you've been
beaten so badly by humans.

00:14:15.880 --> 00:14:16.750
How useless.

00:14:30.760 --> 00:14:32.090
Now that's more like it.

00:15:09.910 --> 00:15:11.150
Human tactics

00:15:11.150 --> 00:15:13.350
have indeed improved quite a bit.

00:15:24.270 --> 00:15:24.840
My Lord!

00:15:24.980 --> 00:15:25.650
We can't win!

00:15:25.650 --> 00:15:26.510
Let's retreat!

00:15:26.510 --> 00:15:28.310
If we don't, they'll kill us all!

00:15:32.270 --> 00:15:32.870
Fall back.

00:15:35.670 --> 00:15:36.200
Go!

00:15:36.710 --> 00:15:37.430
Run!

00:15:37.870 --> 00:15:38.480
Tan'er,

00:15:38.620 --> 00:15:40.420
protect your brother and leave!

00:15:42.840 --> 00:15:43.550
Come on!

00:15:48.020 --> 00:15:49.750
Don't pursue a cornered enemy.

00:15:50.150 --> 00:15:51.950
The humans have grown stronger,

00:15:52.010 --> 00:15:53.930
but they're not unbeatable yet.

00:15:54.200 --> 00:15:55.580
He was scared off?

00:15:56.390 --> 00:15:57.600
But Hong Ye is

00:15:58.490 --> 00:15:59.690
really something now

00:16:01.250 --> 00:16:02.820
after 10,000 years.

00:16:05.550 --> 00:16:06.480
Shut your mouth!

00:16:06.930 --> 00:16:09.390
How dare you speak so carelessly
about His Lordship?

00:16:09.390 --> 00:16:12.320
Little cat demon,
you're quite protective of your master.

00:16:12.320 --> 00:16:14.050
The humans have retreated now.

00:16:14.390 --> 00:16:15.270
Take everyone

00:16:15.270 --> 00:16:16.320
to a safe place.

00:16:17.910 --> 00:16:18.440
Let's go.

00:16:19.320 --> 00:16:20.480
Follow me to the Moon-Gazing Terrace.

00:16:20.480 --> 00:16:20.910
Mm.

00:16:24.750 --> 00:16:26.610
Fortunately, I reacted quickly.

00:16:26.630 --> 00:16:27.750
Otherwise, I would've been done for.

00:16:27.750 --> 00:16:28.690
Had I not been injured,

00:16:28.690 --> 00:16:29.690
this would have been
a piece of cake for me.

00:16:29.690 --> 00:16:30.420
Are you okay?

00:16:30.600 --> 00:16:31.670
I'm okay. Just some minor wounds.

00:16:31.670 --> 00:16:32.270
You doing alright?

00:16:32.270 --> 00:16:33.010
Yeah.

00:16:33.340 --> 00:16:34.670
How's your injury here?

00:16:34.760 --> 00:16:35.220
Come on.

00:16:38.240 --> 00:16:39.080
It doesn't hurt anymore.

00:16:39.080 --> 00:16:39.830
Thank you.

00:16:39.870 --> 00:16:41.440
-Don't worry. I'm fine.
-His Lordship is back.

00:16:41.440 --> 00:16:42.840
-My Lord.
-And Xiao Yao is back, too.

00:16:42.840 --> 00:16:43.470
Xiao Yao.

00:16:43.510 --> 00:16:44.100
My Lord.

00:16:44.120 --> 00:16:44.640
My Lord.

00:16:45.080 --> 00:16:45.880
My Lord.

00:16:46.370 --> 00:16:47.570
-My Lord.
-Xiao Ming.

00:16:50.950 --> 00:16:52.950
You've got your power back, My Lord?

00:16:54.250 --> 00:16:55.960
His Lordship has restored his power!

00:16:55.960 --> 00:16:56.440
Really?

00:16:56.440 --> 00:16:57.270
That's great!

00:16:57.270 --> 00:16:58.230
Sorry,

00:16:58.370 --> 00:17:00.030
everyone, I've come too late.

00:17:06.310 --> 00:17:09.170
Thank you
for your tremendous help, seniors.

00:17:09.190 --> 00:17:10.490
As expected of great senior demons.

00:17:10.490 --> 00:17:11.550
You can tell the difference

00:17:11.550 --> 00:17:12.960
when senior demons strike.

00:17:12.960 --> 00:17:14.270
You've truly opened our eyes.

00:17:14.270 --> 00:17:14.880
Xiao Yao,

00:17:15.349 --> 00:17:16.280
I told you before

00:17:16.690 --> 00:17:18.020
that even without Hong Ye,

00:17:18.020 --> 00:17:19.819
we could still repel the humans.

00:17:20.829 --> 00:17:21.349
Hong Ye,

00:17:21.880 --> 00:17:23.410
the humans have retreated.

00:17:23.640 --> 00:17:24.200
Now,

00:17:24.490 --> 00:17:26.180
it's time to settle our score.

00:17:28.069 --> 00:17:29.870
Regardless of our past grudges,

00:17:30.150 --> 00:17:31.810
I, Hong Ye, really appreciate

00:17:32.150 --> 00:17:33.410
your tremendous help.

00:17:40.610 --> 00:17:41.160
Xiao Ming.

00:17:41.160 --> 00:17:41.590
Yes.

00:17:41.940 --> 00:17:43.200
Take everyone back to Youning Cave.

00:17:43.200 --> 00:17:44.400
I need to discuss important matters

00:17:44.400 --> 00:17:45.260
with these 3 seniors.

00:17:45.260 --> 00:17:45.830
But...

00:17:46.370 --> 00:17:47.400
Follow my order.

00:17:48.510 --> 00:17:49.220
Yes.

00:17:50.200 --> 00:17:52.240
Everyone, follow me back to Youning Cave!

00:17:52.240 --> 00:17:52.850
Let's go.

00:17:52.870 --> 00:17:54.200
Come on, let me help you.

00:18:01.840 --> 00:18:02.770
I'm not leaving.

00:18:03.550 --> 00:18:04.220
Xiao Yao.

00:18:04.920 --> 00:18:05.580
Step aside.

00:18:06.480 --> 00:18:07.740
This is between Hong Ye

00:18:08.120 --> 00:18:09.550
and the 3 of us.

00:18:10.510 --> 00:18:11.040
Xiao Yao,

00:18:11.710 --> 00:18:12.540
he's right.

00:18:12.590 --> 00:18:15.000
Though I don't know
what happened in the past,

00:18:15.000 --> 00:18:15.780
today,

00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:18.500
I must settle things with these 3.

00:18:22.510 --> 00:18:23.170
Let me do it.

00:18:23.880 --> 00:18:24.460
You!

00:18:30.070 --> 00:18:30.920
What are you looking at?

00:18:30.920 --> 00:18:32.110
I'm talking to you.

00:18:32.350 --> 00:18:33.080
What did I do?

00:18:33.200 --> 00:18:35.400
I won't talk
about past grievances for now.

00:18:35.400 --> 00:18:36.550
You just held me hostage,

00:18:36.550 --> 00:18:37.640
nearly ruining my reputation.

00:18:37.640 --> 00:18:39.900
How do we settle this immediate offense?

00:18:41.030 --> 00:18:42.380
When did I ever hold you hostage?

00:18:42.380 --> 00:18:44.110
You took advantage of the chaos,

00:18:44.110 --> 00:18:46.400
and your methods weren't
any better than humans'.

00:18:46.400 --> 00:18:48.750
You weren't really trying
to ruin my sister's reputation, were you?

00:18:48.750 --> 00:18:49.430
Nonsense!

00:18:49.720 --> 00:18:50.790
I was afraid you two would hurt her.

00:18:50.790 --> 00:18:51.510
That's right.

00:18:51.510 --> 00:18:52.590
You almost hurt her.

00:18:52.590 --> 00:18:53.790
When did I ever hurt her?

00:18:53.790 --> 00:18:54.320
He's mad,

00:18:54.550 --> 00:18:55.110
getting defensive!

00:18:55.110 --> 00:18:56.110
Why so mad?

00:18:56.110 --> 00:18:56.960
Who's mad?

00:18:56.980 --> 00:18:58.380
And you two...

00:18:58.920 --> 00:18:59.490
Sister,

00:18:59.640 --> 00:19:01.420
I always listen to you.

00:19:01.640 --> 00:19:02.160
Me, too...

00:19:02.160 --> 00:19:02.790
Shut up.

00:19:05.680 --> 00:19:07.080
What did you just call me?

00:19:07.480 --> 00:19:08.540
Sister, of course.

00:19:09.020 --> 00:19:10.490
I've missed you so much.

00:19:11.640 --> 00:19:12.530
Shameless.

00:19:17.690 --> 00:19:19.270
Since you call me sister,

00:19:19.550 --> 00:19:21.400
why are you irritating me here

00:19:21.400 --> 00:19:22.530
just like these two?

00:19:25.240 --> 00:19:27.040
There's indeed something wrong

00:19:27.110 --> 00:19:28.000
with you two.

00:19:45.070 --> 00:19:45.930
Hong Ye!

00:19:47.680 --> 00:19:49.800
How dare you hide behind Xiao Yao?

00:19:50.440 --> 00:19:52.350
Today, I challenge you
to a fight to the death.

00:19:52.350 --> 00:19:53.550
Do you dare accept it?

00:19:53.640 --> 00:19:54.480
I'll say yes.

00:19:55.070 --> 00:19:56.660
I challenge you to a fight.

00:19:57.110 --> 00:19:58.310
Do you dare accept it?

00:19:58.840 --> 00:19:59.300
Come on.

00:19:59.480 --> 00:20:00.480
Fight me first.

00:20:00.750 --> 00:20:02.350
Then you can go fight Hong Ye.

00:20:04.540 --> 00:20:05.140
Well...

00:20:06.270 --> 00:20:07.160
"Well"?

00:20:07.180 --> 00:20:08.110
Are you dumb?

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:11.910
What?

00:20:12.070 --> 00:20:12.590
Are you scared?

00:20:12.590 --> 00:20:12.990
Why...

00:20:13.680 --> 00:20:14.440
Why wouldn't I be scared?

00:20:14.440 --> 00:20:15.840
So, will you fight or not?

00:20:22.270 --> 00:20:24.310
I was just released
from a 10,000-year seal.

00:20:24.310 --> 00:20:25.190
My body is

00:20:25.310 --> 00:20:25.790
weak.

00:20:26.510 --> 00:20:28.570
Let me recover first before we fight.

00:20:29.070 --> 00:20:29.930
What do you say?

00:20:31.030 --> 00:20:31.750
Fine!

00:20:35.200 --> 00:20:36.330
What about you then?

00:20:36.640 --> 00:20:38.100
Need some time to recover?

00:20:43.700 --> 00:20:45.710
Our Demons' Valley has been destroyed.

00:20:45.710 --> 00:20:47.150
We need to rebuild our home.

00:20:47.150 --> 00:20:48.600
There are a whole lot of things
to attend to.

00:20:48.600 --> 00:20:50.330
So we'll have to take our leave.

00:20:51.210 --> 00:20:51.830
Let's go.

00:20:56.240 --> 00:20:56.710
Xiao...

00:21:02.790 --> 00:21:03.200
To...

00:21:03.530 --> 00:21:04.470
To kill Hong Ye,

00:21:04.830 --> 00:21:06.430
we must first fight Xiao Yao.

00:21:06.920 --> 00:21:08.120
Isn't it unsolvable?

00:21:09.160 --> 00:21:10.790
The Qiong Qi Clan has robust limbs

00:21:10.790 --> 00:21:11.790
but simple minds.

00:21:12.090 --> 00:21:14.020
The reputation is well-deserved.

00:21:18.590 --> 00:21:19.380
Enough!

00:21:19.640 --> 00:21:20.900
You still don't get it?

00:21:21.030 --> 00:21:22.240
Even without her memory,

00:21:22.240 --> 00:21:23.510
Sister is still protecting Hong Ye.

00:21:23.510 --> 00:21:24.240
That means

00:21:24.750 --> 00:21:26.010
even if we kill Hong Ye,

00:21:26.640 --> 00:21:28.270
Sister will only resent us.

00:21:29.030 --> 00:21:30.890
We need to figure out another way.

00:21:31.310 --> 00:21:32.720
What's most frustrating now is

00:21:32.720 --> 00:21:35.250
that even Hong Ye
doesn't remember anything.

00:21:35.400 --> 00:21:36.480
Even if I kill him,

00:21:37.270 --> 00:21:39.600
it still won't
ease the hatred in my heart!

00:21:44.960 --> 00:21:47.430
How did those 3 show up
out of nowhere again?

00:21:47.770 --> 00:21:49.690
These 3 great demons are powerful

00:21:50.350 --> 00:21:51.750
and harbor intense resentment

00:21:51.750 --> 00:21:53.480
toward both humans and demons.

00:21:53.590 --> 00:21:55.920
They were sealed in Yunmeng Lake years ago

00:21:56.030 --> 00:21:58.400
for fear that they would bring disaster
to the world.

00:21:58.400 --> 00:21:59.400
But this matter is

00:21:59.430 --> 00:22:00.890
a secret of the demon race,

00:22:01.050 --> 00:22:03.180
known only to successive Demon Kings.

00:22:03.480 --> 00:22:04.640
Yet somehow Heiwu

00:22:04.880 --> 00:22:06.360
learned about this secret

00:22:06.920 --> 00:22:08.260
and broke their seal.

00:22:12.510 --> 00:22:14.910
They actually are quite adorable, though.

00:22:14.920 --> 00:22:17.050
Who knows if they're just pretending?

00:22:21.700 --> 00:22:24.010
Why are they so hostile toward you?

00:22:27.880 --> 00:22:29.140
I wonder what grudges

00:22:29.750 --> 00:22:31.210
existed 10,000 years ago.

00:22:31.840 --> 00:22:33.970
So we knew each other 10,000 years ago.

00:22:34.640 --> 00:22:35.660
I'm so curious

00:22:35.690 --> 00:22:37.890
about how we first met 10,000 years ago.

00:22:44.200 --> 00:22:45.260
Exalted Immortal.

00:22:46.720 --> 00:22:48.650
We've heard that you consume wind and dew

00:22:48.650 --> 00:22:50.620
and gather the essence of flowers.

00:22:50.920 --> 00:22:53.110
So we have prepared
these humble offerings,

00:22:53.110 --> 00:22:54.950
hoping they might

00:22:55.720 --> 00:22:57.680
please you, Exalted Immortal.

00:23:10.700 --> 00:23:12.300
You dare speak of sincerity?

00:23:14.830 --> 00:23:16.890
I guess it was your unsatisfied greed

00:23:17.130 --> 00:23:19.060
that caused you this retribution!

00:23:21.160 --> 00:23:22.220
Exalted Immortal,

00:23:22.510 --> 00:23:24.010
why do you say so?

00:23:25.110 --> 00:23:27.510
The Emperor trusted shameless sorcerers,

00:23:27.830 --> 00:23:29.100
misused pills,

00:23:29.880 --> 00:23:31.740
and consumed way too many demons,

00:23:31.780 --> 00:23:34.310
leading to the emergence
of the ancient great demons

00:23:34.310 --> 00:23:35.640
who had been sealed for 10,000 years.

00:23:35.640 --> 00:23:37.550
How could humans stand a chance to win?

00:23:37.550 --> 00:23:37.970
Well...

00:23:37.970 --> 00:23:39.240
How could this happen?

00:23:39.920 --> 00:23:41.400
Please calm down, Exalted Immortal.

00:23:41.400 --> 00:23:43.400
I'm going to petition His Majesty

00:23:43.400 --> 00:23:44.710
to send reinforcements immediately.

00:23:44.710 --> 00:23:46.250
All hell broke loose.

00:23:47.200 --> 00:23:49.130
No matter how many troops you send,

00:23:50.370 --> 00:23:53.050
they won't satisfy
the demons' bloodthirst.

00:23:55.070 --> 00:23:58.140
Please save us, Exalted Immortal!

00:24:09.630 --> 00:24:10.660
Is there

00:24:11.920 --> 00:24:13.530
a Mountain and Sea Map

00:24:14.110 --> 00:24:16.770
drawn by ancient demons
in the imperial palace?

00:24:20.110 --> 00:24:21.960
Go check
the imperial treasury immediately.

00:24:21.960 --> 00:24:22.710
If it's there,

00:24:22.710 --> 00:24:25.310
bring it
to the Exalted Immortal immediately!

00:24:25.990 --> 00:24:26.710
Hurry!

00:24:27.400 --> 00:24:28.060
-Yes.
-Yes.

00:24:28.390 --> 00:24:29.190
Hurry up!

00:24:32.240 --> 00:24:32.740
Get up.

00:24:33.070 --> 00:24:33.670
Leave now.

00:25:30.660 --> 00:25:31.920
Dreamshard Immortal,

00:25:34.030 --> 00:25:36.030
I ended up becoming you.

00:25:41.610 --> 00:25:42.090
No!

00:25:44.100 --> 00:25:44.900
I am not you.

00:25:47.160 --> 00:25:48.640
I will never become you!

00:26:03.510 --> 00:26:04.510
You may all leave.

00:26:06.830 --> 00:26:07.490
-Yes.
-Yes.

00:26:25.240 --> 00:26:28.290
[Misty Forest] [Mount Qingyuan]
[Mount Qingyun] [Pingjiang Prefecture]

00:26:28.310 --> 00:26:32.300
[Hong Ye] [Qiong Qi] [Ao Hen] [Teng She]

00:26:35.150 --> 00:26:37.400
[Hong Ye] [Qiong Qi] [Ao Hen] [Teng She]

00:26:37.400 --> 00:26:39.000
There are actually 3 of them.

00:26:41.510 --> 00:26:42.720
No wonder we lost.

00:26:54.390 --> 00:26:56.220
We were originally prepared
to deal with Hong Ye alone,

00:26:56.220 --> 00:26:57.630
but now there are 3 more.

00:26:58.840 --> 00:27:00.870
Each of them is
even more powerful than Hong Ye.

00:27:00.870 --> 00:27:02.530
How can we continue fighting?

00:27:03.010 --> 00:27:05.070
The Bulwark Duke is working on a plan.

00:27:05.480 --> 00:27:06.200
We just

00:27:06.750 --> 00:27:07.880
need to follow orders.

00:27:07.880 --> 00:27:08.310
Mm.

00:27:14.920 --> 00:27:15.350
Sir,

00:27:15.930 --> 00:27:17.480
we've lost everything we had.

00:27:17.480 --> 00:27:19.540
What plan could we possibly work out?

00:27:22.240 --> 00:27:24.170
Let's count our casualties first.

00:27:24.590 --> 00:27:25.000
Yes.

00:27:34.140 --> 00:27:35.140
You bold demon!

00:27:35.440 --> 00:27:37.700
How dare you sneak into our camp at night?

00:27:41.160 --> 00:27:42.960
Why so nervous, Mr. Ji?

00:27:44.440 --> 00:27:46.240
You and I are now of the same kind.

00:27:47.160 --> 00:27:49.990
Why should I hold past grudges
against you?

00:27:52.590 --> 00:27:54.190
What happened before wasn't

00:27:55.000 --> 00:27:57.070
solely your responsibility.

00:27:58.590 --> 00:28:00.270
I was foolish,

00:28:01.440 --> 00:28:03.720
choosing someone whose word meant nothing

00:28:03.720 --> 00:28:05.590
to join me for the great cause!

00:28:13.560 --> 00:28:15.650
If you go back now,

00:28:16.790 --> 00:28:18.920
humans will surely despise you.

00:28:20.100 --> 00:28:21.580
If I'm not mistaken,

00:28:22.270 --> 00:28:24.730
you won't even be allowed
to survive, right?

00:28:25.240 --> 00:28:28.110
And since Demons' Valley
cannot be conquered at the moment,

00:28:28.110 --> 00:28:31.140
you're truly caught
between a rock and a hard place.

00:28:34.720 --> 00:28:37.110
But we're in the same situation.

00:28:38.400 --> 00:28:40.460
Neither humans nor demons accept us.

00:28:40.790 --> 00:28:42.680
Only by joining forces

00:28:43.910 --> 00:28:46.060
can we gain freedom of movement.

00:28:46.920 --> 00:28:48.240
You need me.

00:28:49.880 --> 00:28:52.190
Because I know demons the best.

00:28:54.070 --> 00:28:55.530
Come into the tent to talk.

00:29:12.160 --> 00:29:12.640
My Lord,

00:29:13.110 --> 00:29:14.240
Heiwu was previously

00:29:14.240 --> 00:29:15.350
my informant

00:29:15.350 --> 00:29:16.960
planted among the demons.

00:29:18.590 --> 00:29:19.390
Informant?

00:29:21.400 --> 00:29:22.420
Is he an informant

00:29:22.680 --> 00:29:24.000
or just a loser?

00:29:26.240 --> 00:29:28.770
I've offended you a lot before,
Bulwark Duke.

00:29:29.030 --> 00:29:30.630
I'd like to apologize for it.

00:29:31.000 --> 00:29:31.790
Hope you

00:29:33.070 --> 00:29:34.600
can let it go, Bulwark Duke.

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:38.300
This defeat

00:29:38.880 --> 00:29:40.680
has caused humans heavy losses.

00:29:41.350 --> 00:29:43.270
Aren't you curious, Bulwark Duke,

00:29:43.270 --> 00:29:46.400
about the 3 great demons
that suddenly appeared in Demons' Valley

00:29:46.400 --> 00:29:47.830
and their origins?

00:29:54.480 --> 00:29:55.340
There used to be

00:29:55.590 --> 00:29:57.450
a Sea Turtle guarding this place,

00:29:57.590 --> 00:29:59.120
so the seal never weakened.

00:30:00.440 --> 00:30:02.900
To release
those 3 ancient fierce beasts,

00:30:03.710 --> 00:30:05.510
Hong Ye used any means necessary

00:30:06.030 --> 00:30:08.890
and cruelly murdered
the only Demon Lord Sea Turtle

00:30:09.200 --> 00:30:10.370
of our demons.

00:30:14.680 --> 00:30:16.210
Sea Turtle above in heaven,

00:30:17.110 --> 00:30:18.480
I, Heiwu,

00:30:19.000 --> 00:30:20.870
will surely avenge your death!

00:30:29.590 --> 00:30:30.720
Those 3 great demons

00:30:31.920 --> 00:30:33.880
in yesterday's battle all have power

00:30:33.880 --> 00:30:35.240
greater than Hong Ye's.

00:30:36.880 --> 00:30:38.800
Even if Hong Ye removed the seal

00:30:39.000 --> 00:30:40.730
to bring disaster to the world,

00:30:41.680 --> 00:30:42.480
how could he possibly

00:30:42.480 --> 00:30:45.140
control 3 ancient fierce beasts
at the same time

00:30:45.390 --> 00:30:46.460
to work for him?

00:30:49.270 --> 00:30:50.480
Xiao Yao.

00:30:53.120 --> 00:30:54.080
Xiao Yao?

00:30:54.350 --> 00:30:56.210
I saw it with my own eyes yesterday

00:30:56.510 --> 00:30:59.030
that those 3 great demons were all
devoted to Xiao Yao.

00:30:59.030 --> 00:31:00.540
Xiao Yao said a few words,

00:31:00.750 --> 00:31:01.960
yet they took them as gospel

00:31:01.960 --> 00:31:03.290
and obeyed completely.

00:31:03.510 --> 00:31:04.160
I guess

00:31:04.680 --> 00:31:06.470
Hong Ye exploited this

00:31:06.720 --> 00:31:07.790
to trick them

00:31:08.620 --> 00:31:09.970
into fighting for him.

00:31:20.660 --> 00:31:23.480
When Tan'er fought those 3 great demons,

00:31:24.030 --> 00:31:26.000
I could sense their power, too.

00:31:27.000 --> 00:31:29.200
They truly boast tremendous strength.

00:31:29.240 --> 00:31:31.970
With these 3 ancient great demons
joining the demon side,

00:31:31.970 --> 00:31:34.300
humans are now greatly outmatched.

00:31:34.510 --> 00:31:36.770
You cannot hope to win by strength alone.

00:31:37.890 --> 00:31:39.530
You must find their weakness

00:31:40.730 --> 00:31:42.190
and defeat them one by one.

00:31:42.270 --> 00:31:44.550
Heiwu's selfish intentions are obvious.

00:31:44.550 --> 00:31:47.350
He simply wants to use human power
for his own ends.

00:31:47.830 --> 00:31:49.560
Be it humans or demons,

00:31:50.440 --> 00:31:52.170
everyone has selfish motives.

00:31:52.570 --> 00:31:54.570
Since you know his true intentions,

00:31:55.580 --> 00:31:56.640
you should realize

00:31:57.550 --> 00:31:58.950
that what he says is true.

00:31:59.440 --> 00:32:01.300
The 3 ancient great demons

00:32:01.870 --> 00:32:03.080
plus Hong Ye.

00:32:04.240 --> 00:32:05.030
They've got

00:32:08.360 --> 00:32:09.660
only one weakness.

00:32:22.440 --> 00:32:23.770
What on earth happened?

00:32:34.480 --> 00:32:35.500
Exalted Immortal,

00:32:35.500 --> 00:32:36.430
are you alright?

00:32:42.350 --> 00:32:43.400
Blood essence...

00:32:45.080 --> 00:32:46.420
Spiritual essence...

00:32:59.200 --> 00:33:00.260
Exalted Immortal,

00:33:00.500 --> 00:33:01.300
drink this.

00:33:12.590 --> 00:33:14.090
Get lost now.

00:33:16.960 --> 00:33:17.640
Yes.

00:33:24.430 --> 00:33:25.430
Immortal Lord...

00:33:28.440 --> 00:33:30.400
I will never become you.

00:33:32.510 --> 00:33:33.790
Never!

00:33:38.840 --> 00:33:39.640
Bulwark Duke.

00:33:39.950 --> 00:33:41.110
What happened, Bulwark Duke?

00:33:41.110 --> 00:33:42.680
There's an emergency happening
in the capital.

00:33:42.680 --> 00:33:44.000
I must hurry back immediately.

00:33:44.000 --> 00:33:44.720
Bulwark Duke,

00:33:44.720 --> 00:33:45.590
you can't do it.

00:33:45.680 --> 00:33:47.240
The war
between the 2 clans is ever-changing.

00:33:47.240 --> 00:33:48.440
Any delay could lead to disaster.

00:33:48.440 --> 00:33:50.370
I said I must return to the capital!

00:34:04.640 --> 00:34:06.050
What on earth happened?

00:34:06.240 --> 00:34:07.270
Are you hurt?

00:34:08.030 --> 00:34:08.960
I'm fine.

00:34:10.150 --> 00:34:11.350
The war is important.

00:34:12.070 --> 00:34:13.360
Do not be distracted.

00:34:14.880 --> 00:34:16.630
You're alone in the capital.

00:34:16.630 --> 00:34:18.190
Everyone is keeping an eye on you.

00:34:18.190 --> 00:34:19.489
How can I not worry?

00:34:20.710 --> 00:34:23.370
I am the Exalted Immortal
in the Emperor's eyes.

00:34:24.030 --> 00:34:25.710
Who would dare harm me?

00:34:27.060 --> 00:34:28.389
Even if I die,

00:34:30.030 --> 00:34:32.590
I will never consume
other people's essence

00:34:33.400 --> 00:34:36.000
or do things
that would make you look down on me.

00:34:39.840 --> 00:34:41.440
Everything will be fine

00:34:43.670 --> 00:34:45.230
once I find the Yuli Spring.

00:34:49.400 --> 00:34:50.920
It's just that lately,

00:34:53.760 --> 00:34:55.070
I often feel...

00:34:57.660 --> 00:35:00.320
I feel
that Dreamshard Immortal is still alive.

00:35:01.230 --> 00:35:02.980
She's in my body,

00:35:03.230 --> 00:35:04.710
trying to consume me,

00:35:06.440 --> 00:35:07.690
to enslave me,

00:35:09.690 --> 00:35:11.810
until she completely devours me.

00:35:13.150 --> 00:35:14.000
Bingzhu,

00:35:15.150 --> 00:35:16.150
do you remember

00:35:18.110 --> 00:35:20.000
when you first met me?

00:35:21.490 --> 00:35:22.960
As if it were yesterday.

00:35:25.710 --> 00:35:26.750
Great.

00:35:30.180 --> 00:35:31.390
I thought

00:35:35.370 --> 00:35:37.890
it had been
hundreds or thousands of years.

00:35:39.280 --> 00:35:41.810
Because even I
can barely remember it myself.

00:35:44.230 --> 00:35:46.280
This is all my fault.

00:35:46.880 --> 00:35:49.810
Everything I've done wasn't
to make you feel guilty.

00:35:50.960 --> 00:35:51.710
I know.

00:35:56.630 --> 00:35:57.670
You once said...

00:36:00.760 --> 00:36:02.960
You would take care of me for my brother.

00:36:05.320 --> 00:36:06.580
Does that still stand?

00:36:09.110 --> 00:36:10.190
Yes, of course.

00:36:13.800 --> 00:36:16.320
If you help me fulfill 3 more wishes,

00:36:18.920 --> 00:36:20.050
that will be enough.

00:36:23.070 --> 00:36:23.710
Okay.

00:36:25.480 --> 00:36:26.070
Go ahead.

00:36:27.960 --> 00:36:29.960
You said that you raised Tan'er.

00:36:31.280 --> 00:36:33.880
When she was little,
you couldn't afford toys,

00:36:33.930 --> 00:36:35.550
so you used your knife

00:36:36.240 --> 00:36:38.830
to carve wooden and bamboo dolls

00:36:39.670 --> 00:36:40.920
to make her happy

00:36:41.800 --> 00:36:43.000
and help her sleep.

00:36:46.440 --> 00:36:47.400
Could you...

00:36:50.190 --> 00:36:51.670
carve one for me, too?

00:36:54.510 --> 00:36:55.320
Of course.

00:36:57.480 --> 00:36:59.680
What kind of wooden doll would you like?

00:37:04.230 --> 00:37:05.230
Just make one

00:37:08.590 --> 00:37:10.030
that looks like me

00:37:13.500 --> 00:37:14.790
when we first met.

00:37:16.260 --> 00:37:17.590
Do you still remember?

00:37:19.690 --> 00:37:21.000
Of course I do.

00:37:23.950 --> 00:37:25.750
And what about your second wish?

00:37:27.250 --> 00:37:28.080
What's it?

00:37:31.440 --> 00:37:31.960
I...

00:37:32.110 --> 00:37:33.710
I can't think of it right now.

00:37:35.880 --> 00:37:37.760
When I think of something,

00:37:39.420 --> 00:37:40.670
I'll let you know.

00:37:58.920 --> 00:37:59.760
Orioles,

00:38:00.760 --> 00:38:01.550
Parrot,

00:38:02.590 --> 00:38:04.800
I can't bring you back to life,

00:38:05.970 --> 00:38:07.550
but together, we can

00:38:07.880 --> 00:38:09.590
save these dying flowers.

00:38:18.360 --> 00:38:20.690
You're quite good at deceiving yourself.

00:38:22.790 --> 00:38:24.050
Why are you still here?

00:38:25.310 --> 00:38:27.040
I just won a battle for you guys,

00:38:27.340 --> 00:38:29.070
and now you want to cut me loose?

00:38:33.370 --> 00:38:35.170
If these birds were still alive,

00:38:35.490 --> 00:38:37.290
would they agree to what you did?

00:38:37.730 --> 00:38:39.510
You turned their original bodies

00:38:39.510 --> 00:38:41.050
into rotten fertilizers

00:38:41.360 --> 00:38:42.960
to nourish a useless flower.

00:38:44.550 --> 00:38:46.400
All things in the world are one.

00:38:46.510 --> 00:38:47.480
As one wanes, another waxes.

00:38:47.480 --> 00:38:48.400
They nourish each other

00:38:48.400 --> 00:38:49.660
to achieve longevity.

00:38:49.710 --> 00:38:51.110
This is the law of nature.

00:38:51.150 --> 00:38:53.280
How can you call it rotten and useless?

00:38:53.590 --> 00:38:55.320
What a fine talk of wane and wax.

00:38:56.230 --> 00:38:57.710
Then, if Hong Ye's death

00:38:58.000 --> 00:38:59.840
could bring prosperity to demons,

00:38:59.840 --> 00:39:00.710
would you do it?

00:39:03.320 --> 00:39:04.520
Only with Hong Ye here

00:39:04.550 --> 00:39:05.760
will demons prosper.

00:39:07.360 --> 00:39:08.680
Were it not for Hong Ye,

00:39:09.150 --> 00:39:11.480
humans would have already been wiped out.

00:39:11.510 --> 00:39:12.230
And demons

00:39:12.840 --> 00:39:14.970
wouldn't be in such a miserable state.

00:39:16.400 --> 00:39:18.400
I'm afraid Hong Ye has never told you

00:39:18.710 --> 00:39:20.710
how he became the Demon King, right?

00:39:22.670 --> 00:39:23.670
Does that matter?

00:39:24.250 --> 00:39:26.000
You don't need to sow discord here.

00:39:26.000 --> 00:39:27.230
He's entirely devoted
to protecting demons,

00:39:27.230 --> 00:39:29.230
exhausting himself for their sake.

00:39:29.480 --> 00:39:30.340
That's enough.

00:39:31.630 --> 00:39:32.760
You don't remember,

00:39:34.960 --> 00:39:36.620
so it doesn't matter anymore?

00:39:47.230 --> 00:39:47.890
Never mind.

00:39:48.800 --> 00:39:50.460
I've waited for 10,000 years.

00:39:50.920 --> 00:39:53.120
A few more days won't make a difference.

00:39:54.480 --> 00:39:55.940
But you'd better remember

00:39:56.680 --> 00:39:58.740
that I, Ao Hen, always get my revenge.

00:39:59.480 --> 00:40:01.010
You can protect him for now,

00:40:01.960 --> 00:40:03.070
but not forever.

00:40:14.000 --> 00:40:14.670
Sister!

00:40:15.360 --> 00:40:15.960
Sister,

00:40:16.150 --> 00:40:16.630
look!

00:40:16.960 --> 00:40:18.220
See what I brought you.

00:40:20.400 --> 00:40:22.860
Why did you bring
the Zhuyu herbs' home here?

00:40:23.030 --> 00:40:25.550
I thought
these little things were quite cute,

00:40:25.550 --> 00:40:26.630
and you might like...

00:40:26.630 --> 00:40:27.360
Put it back!

00:40:30.510 --> 00:40:32.030
That's what you get
for flattering her recklessly!

00:40:32.030 --> 00:40:33.360
You irritated her, huh?

00:40:39.230 --> 00:40:40.000
Alright, alright.

00:40:40.000 --> 00:40:41.480
I'm not really mad.

00:40:41.480 --> 00:40:42.800
You're actually quite adorable.

00:40:42.800 --> 00:40:43.480
Much better than

00:40:43.480 --> 00:40:45.150
that sarcastic Ao Hen.

00:40:45.880 --> 00:40:46.440
Xiao Yao,

00:40:46.880 --> 00:40:48.540
has Ao Hen provoked you again?

00:40:49.440 --> 00:40:50.400
No, no, no.

00:40:50.400 --> 00:40:51.000
Well,

00:40:51.510 --> 00:40:53.190
it's because of my weak power.

00:40:53.230 --> 00:40:54.800
It has nothing to do with the senior.

00:40:54.800 --> 00:40:55.670
It doesn't matter.

00:40:55.670 --> 00:40:56.800
As long as we're here,

00:40:56.800 --> 00:40:58.400
you're still the strongest in this world.

00:40:58.400 --> 00:40:58.880
Mm.

00:41:00.400 --> 00:41:01.590
I appreciate your kindness,

00:41:01.590 --> 00:41:04.120
but I think it's better
to cultivate on my own.

00:41:05.280 --> 00:41:06.030
Well, then,

00:41:06.400 --> 00:41:07.920
let me teach you, Sister.

00:41:09.480 --> 00:41:10.110
Um,

00:41:10.590 --> 00:41:12.850
could you please stop calling me Sister?

00:41:14.150 --> 00:41:15.400
You said it for real?

00:41:15.670 --> 00:41:16.280
So,

00:41:16.360 --> 00:41:17.820
if I don't call you Sister,

00:41:17.880 --> 00:41:18.880
does that mean...

00:41:18.880 --> 00:41:20.630
Does that mean I can like you now?

00:41:20.630 --> 00:41:21.670
What nonsense are you talking about?